Package: spatrans
Type: Package
Title: Analyze Spatial Transcriptomics and Other Spatial Omics Data on the Single Molecule Scale
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Stijn", family = "Hawinkel", 
    email = "stijn.hawinkel@psb.ugent.be", 
    role=c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4501-5180")))
Description: Test for univariate and multivariate spatial patterns in 
    spatial omics data with single-molecule resolution. The tests implemented 
    allow for analysis of nested designs and are automatically calibrated to different
    biological specimens. Tests for aggregation, colocalization and vicinity to cell edge are provided.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: spatstat.geom, spatstat.random, SpatialExperiment, methods, BiocParallel, SummarizedExperiment, scam, Rdpack, proxy, stats, utils, Rfast, extraDistr,lmerTest,lme4,ggplot2,graphics,grDevices,Rcpp (>= 1.0.11)
Suggests: testthat,rmarkdown,knitr,DropletUtils
RdMacros: Rdpack
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
biocViews: Transcriptomics, Spatial, SingleCell
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
